from example.commons import Faker
from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Geo
from pyecharts.globals import ChartType, SymbolType
from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Map


def geo_heatmap() -> Geo:
    c = (
        Geo()
        .add_schema(maptype="china")
        .add(
            "景区个数热力图",
            [list(z) for z in zip(y,x)],
            type_=ChartType.HEATMAP,
        )
        .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False))
        .set_global_opts(
            visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(),
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="景区个数热力图"),
        )
    )
    return c
geo_heatmap().render_notebook()

def geo_base() -> Geo:
    c = (
        Geo()
        .add_schema(maptype="china")
        .add("数量", a)
        .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False))
        .set_global_opts(
            visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(),
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="各省市景区数量图"),
        )
    )
    return c
geo_base().render_notebook()

def geo_guangdong() -> Geo:
    c = (
        Geo()
        .add_schema(maptype="山东")
        .add(
            "geo",
            [list(z) for z in zip(shi[0:7], num[0:7])],
            type_=ChartType.HEATMAP,
        )
        .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(is_show=False))
        .set_global_opts(
            visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(),
            title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="山东景区分布热力图"),
        )
    )
    return c

from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.charts import Funnel, Page


def funnel_base() -> Funnel:
    c = (
        Funnel()
        .add("商品", [list(z) for z in zip(shengfen, ping)])
        .set_global_opts(title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title="门票总数漏斗图"))
    )
    return c

def funnel_sort_ascending() -> Funnel:
